    { question: "What LinkedIn data does EventHex access via OAuth?", answer: "EventHex requests the standard LinkedIn OAuth scopes: name, email address, profile photo, current job title, and employer. No connections, messages, or private data are accessed." },
    { question: "Can attendees still register without a LinkedIn account?", answer: "Yes. LinkedIn social login is an option alongside standard email registration. Attendees can choose their preferred method on the registration page." },
    { question: "How does speaker profile import work?", answer: "You paste a speaker's public LinkedIn profile URL into EventHex. EventHex fetches their name, headshot, current title, employer, and bio summary automatically via the LinkedIn API." },
